message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which holds immense value for us and is worth $12,000 to you. Considering its unique features and benefits, I am offering it to you at an exclusive price of $11,000. This is a special opportunity tailored just for you, aiming to ensure that you receive the best deal possible while maximizing the return on our investment. Please let me know if this offer suits your expectations.
